text = "[center]
Goal:
[p align=center]You need to get to a shaman. In order to do so you need to pickup resources along the way and protect them from thieves while camping.
[/p]
[p align=center]
How to play:
- You select a parrot by clicking on it with LMB
- You move the parrot by clicking on a desired spot with RMB
- You deselect the active parrot by clicking on an empty space with LMB
- The stretcher moves automatically and you need to keep moving with the gatherers or they will be forgotten in the forest and cannot be used until the level ends.
[/p]

[/center]"

